text: Rudolf II (July 18, 1552 - January 20, 1612) was King of Hungary (as Rudolf, 1572-1608), King of Bohemia (as Rudolf II, 1575-1608/1611), Archduke of Austria (as Rudolf V, 1576-1608), and Holy Roman Emperor (as Rudolf II, 1576-1612). He was a member of the Habsburg family. Category:Holy Roman Emperors Category:1552 births Category:1612 deaths Category:16th century in Germany Category:17th century in Germany
title: Rudolf II, Holy Roman Emperor
